                    <a href="/" style="font-size:0.9rem; color:var(--text-muted); text-decoration:none;"><i class="fa-solid fa-xmark"></i> ‡∏•‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏á‡∏Ñ‡πà‡∏≤</a>
